{"tid":521944,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇室戰爭] 韓撚隊友好撚伏啊！？","createTime":"2018-01-07T05:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T05:57:51.000Z","uid":165782,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b03f826d617c2424a3a33205f3baf4a62d2d88","tid":521944,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"起玩皇室戰爭的時候，你會發現同棒子做隊友係最可悲！<br />\n起你形勢大好的時候，即係好似侵侵依家咁當然係無咩問題啦！但係如果起弱勢的時候，例如金仔揮軍南下打咗佢幾個戰略重鎮之後，棒子將會全面崩潰，經常出現中途離場，出賣隊友的情況。<br />\n起現實，難保佢哋會因一時失利而向敵方投降，這就係韓撚垃圾到仆街的民族性。<br />\n他們沒有決戰到底的決心，更加無死戰的勇氣，同佢哋做隊友，伏到核爆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以起隨機配對都加返個國籍選項啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7654cb3e2bc5dc5d4518eb6ac2dd98bac460b7","tid":521944,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"有無咁伏啊？你自己廢無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}